definition.value: A heteropentacyclic compound found in Euphorbia poissonii with molecular formula C36H38O8. It is an agonist of the transient receptor potential cation channel subfamily V member 1 (TrpV1).
A racemate comprising equimolar amounts of (R)- and (S)-tioconazole.

A member of the class of piperidines that is L-tyrosine in which a hydrogen attached to the amino group is replaced by a butylsulfonyl group and in which the hydrogen attached to the phenolic hydroxy group is replaced by a 4-(piperidin-4-yl)butyl group.
